ommunicated solutions for you. These disruptions to the supply chain are unpredictable, but they have caught the attention of Canadian officials in transportation, who are seeing that these issues can grind our trade to a halt. They recognize that to succeed, Canadian businesses need solutions, and not just quick fixes.<\/p>\n<p>If we could wave a magic wand, we would. We can\u2019t, but we can be the next best thing, your buddy for all things borders, supply chains and navigation, no matter what external pressures are thrown at you. <a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/contact\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Let\u2019s chat<\/a> and see how and where we can help streamline your supply chain and control what we can.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If recent trends show anything, it\u2019s that costs are up on almost everything, even doubled, for some goods. There is enormous strain on the whole system, and external crises like supply issues, government requirements and weather disruptions (to name a few) are causing more challenges. What is in your control? Streamlining your supply chain, no&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13,"featured_media":2713,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_genesis_hide_title":false,"_genesis_hide_breadcrumbs":false,"_genesis_hide_singular_image":false,"_genesis_hide_footer_widgets":false,"_genesis_custom_body_class":"","_genesis_custom_post_class":"","_genesis_layout":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v22.4 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Supply Chain Canada: Agility &amp; Streamlining - let\u2019s control what we can &#187; Blog &#187; BorderBuddy<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"If recent trends show anything, it\u2019s that costs are up on almost e